<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />I sought Yahweh and he answered me,</para>

<para style="q1">and he gave me victory over all my fears.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />Those who look to him are radiant,</para>

<para style="q1">and their faces are not ashamed.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />This oppressed man cried and Yahweh heard him</para>

<para style="q1">and saved him from all his troubles.</para>
